== Installation ==

Currently there are several versions of Google Chrome available in the main Gentoo repository:

* {{Package|www-client/google-chrome}} - A stable version of the web browser from Google.
* {{Package|www-client/google-chrome-beta}} - A beta version of the web browser of Google.
* {{Package|www-client/google-chrome-unstable}} - An unstable version of the <s>nightmare</s> web browser from Google.

